"</shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>पूर्वम् विभक्त दृश्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the previous document view, if you have split the editor area in more "
"views."
msgstr "पूर्वदस्तावेजदृश्यं केन्द्रीकुरुत, यदि भवान् सम्पादकक्षेत्रं अधिकदृश्येषु विभक्तवान् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F8</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Next Split View</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F8</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>विभाजनदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>अनन्तरं विभक्तदृश्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the next document view, if you have split the editor area in more "
"views."
msgstr "अग्रिमदस्तावेजदृश्यं केन्द्रीकुरुत, यदि भवान् सम्पादकक्षेत्रं अधिकदृश्येषु विभक्तवान् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Left Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>वामविभक्तदृश्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively on the left, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"विभक्तदृश्यं वामभागे सहजतया केन्द्रीकुरुत, आवश्यके सति अस्पष्टीकरणाय कर्सरस्थानस्य उपयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Right Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>दक्षिणविभक्तदृश्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively on the right, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"विभक्तदृश्यं सहजतया दक्षिणभागे केन्द्रीकुरुत, आवश्यके सति अस्पष्टीकरणाय कर्सरस्थानस्य उपयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Upward Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>ऊर्ध्वविभक्तदृश्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively upward, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"विभक्तदृश्यं सहजतया ऊर्ध्वं केन्द्रीकुरुत, आवश्यके सति अस्पष्टीकरणाय कर्सरस्थानस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Downward Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>अधः "
"विभक्तदृश्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively downward, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"विभक्तदृश्यं सहजतया अधः केन्द्रीकुरुत, आवश्यके सति अस्पष्टीकरणाय कर्सरस्थानस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Split Vertical</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem >विभक्त ऊर्ध्वा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will split the frame (which may be the main editing area) in two "
"equally sized frames, the new one to the left of the current one. The new "
"frame gets the focus, and will display the same document as the old one."
msgstr ""
"एतेन फ्रेम (यत् मुख्यसम्पादनक्षेत्रं भवितुम् अर्हति) समानप्रमाणस्य फ्रेमद्वये विभक्तं भविष्यति, "
"वर्तमानस्य वामभागे नूतनः । नूतनं फ्रेमं फोकस प्राप्नोति, तथा च पुरातनस्य समानं दस्तावेजं "
"प्रदर्शयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:873 menus.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid "See also <link linkend=\"kate-mdi\">Working with the &kate; MDI</link>."
msgstr ""
"अपि द्रष्टव्यम्<link linkend=\"kate-mdi\"> सह कार्यं कुर्वन् &amp;kate; MDI</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Split Horizontal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem >विभक्त क्षैतिज</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Splits the current frame (which may be the main editing area) in two equally "
"sized frames, the new one below the current one. The new frame gets the "
"focus, and displays the same document as the old one."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानचक्रं (यत् मुख्यसम्पादनक्षेत्रं भवितुम् अर्हति) समानप्रमाणस्य फ्रेमद्वये विभजति, वर्तमानस्य "
"अधः नूतनः । नूतनं फ्रेमं फोकस प्राप्नोति, तथा च पुरातनस्य समानं दस्तावेजं प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:889 menus.docbook:917 menus.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid "See also <link linkend=\"kate-mdi\">Working with the &kate; MDI</link>"
msgstr ""
"अपि द्रष्टव्यम्<link linkend=\"kate-mdi\"> सह कार्यं कुर्वन् &amp;kate; MDI</link>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Document to New Vertical Split</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभाजनदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>दस्तावेजं "
"नूतनं ऊर्ध्वाधरविभाजनं</guimenuitem> मध्ये स्थानान्तरयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will split the currently active view vertically into two views and move "
"the currently active document to right view."
msgstr ""
"एतेन वर्तमान सक्रियदृश्यं लम्बवत् द्वयोः दृश्ययोः विभक्तं भविष्यति तथा च वर्तमानं "
"सक्रियदस्तावेजं दक्षिणदृश्यं प्रति स्थानान्तरयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Document to New Horizontal Split</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभाजितदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>दस्तावेजं नूतनक्षैतिजविभाजनं</guimenuitem> मध्ये स्थानान्तरयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will split the currently active view horizontally into two views and "
"move the currently active document to view below."
msgstr ""
"एतेन वर्तमानसक्रियदृश्यं क्षैतिजरूपेण द्वयोः दृश्ययोः विभक्तं भविष्यति तथा च "
"वर्तमानसक्रियदस्तावेजं अधः द्रष्टुं चालयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Toggle Orientation</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>अभिमुखीकरणं टॉगल</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch between horizontal and vertical split."
msgstr "क्षैतिजस्य ऊर्ध्वाधरस्य च विभाजनस्य मध्ये स्विच कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Close Current View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem >वर्तमानदृश्यं बन्दं कुरुत</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes the active frame, which can be identified as the one displaying a "
"blinking cursor. This is disabled, if there is only one frame (the main "
"editing area)."
msgstr ""
"सक्रियं फ्रेमं पिधायति, यत् निमिषं कर्सरं प्रदर्शयति इति परिचयितुं शक्यते । एतत् अक्षमम् अस्ति, "
"यदि केवलम् एकः फ्रेमः (मुख्यसम्पादनक्षेत्रम्) अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:944 menus.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No documents get closed by closing a frame &ndash; they will still be "
"available in the <link linkend=\"view-menu\"><guimenu>View</guimenu> Menu</"
"link> as well as in the File List."
msgstr ""
"एकं फ्रेमं पिधाय कोऽपि दस्तावेजः बन्दः न भवति – ते अद्यापि...<link linkend=\"view-menu"
"\"><guimenu> दृश्यं</guimenu> मेनू</link> तथा च File List इत्यत्र अपि ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Close Inactive Views</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>निष्क्रियदृश्यानि बन्दं कुर्वन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes all frames except the active frame (the one with a blinking cursor). "
"This is disabled, if there is only one frame (the main editing area)."
msgstr ""
"सक्रियं फ्रेम (निमिषमाणं कर्सरयुक्तं) विहाय सर्वाणि फ्रेम्स पिधायति । एतत् अक्षमम् अस्ति, यदि "
"केवलम् एकः फ्रेमः (मुख्यसम्पादनक्षेत्रम्) अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Hide "
"Inactive Views</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>निष्क्रियदृश्यानि गोपयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid "This hides all split views except the currently active one."
msgstr "एतेन वर्तमानं सक्रियं विहाय सर्वाणि विभक्तदृश्यानि गोप्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Left</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>विभाजकं "
"वामभागे स्थानान्तरयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two vertically "
"split documents further left."
msgstr ""
"यदा Split View सक्षमं भवति तदा एतेन द्वयोः लम्बवत् विभक्तदस्तावेजयोः मध्ये सीमां वामभागे "
"गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Right</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>विभाजकं "
"दक्षिणतः चालयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two vertically "
"split documents further right."
msgstr ""
"यदा Split View सक्षमं भवति तदा एतेन द्वयोः लम्बवत् विभक्तदस्तावेजयोः मध्ये सीमा दक्षिणतः "
"गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>विभाजकं "
"उपरि स्थानान्तरयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two "
"horizontally split documents further up."
msgstr ""
"यदा Split View सक्षमं भवति तदा एतेन क्षैतिजरूपेण विभक्तदस्तावेजद्वयस्य सीमां अधिकं उपरि "
"गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Down</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभक्तदृश्य</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>विभाजकं "
"अधः स्थापयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two "
"horizontally split documents further down."
msgstr ""
"यदा Split View सक्षमं भवति तदा एतेन द्वयोः क्षैतिजरूपेण विभक्तदस्तावेजयोः मध्ये सीमा अधः "
"गमिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some common actions in the <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> menu are available using the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-split-"
"left-right-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> button at the top right corner of the editor window"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विभाजितदृश्य</guisubmenu> मेन्यू मध्ये केचन "
"सामान्यक्रियाः <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"view-split-left-right-22 इत्यस्य उपयोगेन उपलभ्यन्ते .png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> बटनं सम्पादकविण्डो इत्यस्य उपरि "
"दक्षिणकोणे अस्ति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>उपकरणदृश्यानि</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap> </"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show Sidebars</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap> </"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>उपकरणदृश्यानि</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>पार्श्वपट्टिकाः दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the sidebar button rows. This command does not affect "
"the display of the sidebar content widgets, any sidebar that is visible will "
"stay visible, and if you assigned shortcuts to the commands below those will "
"of course continue to work."
msgstr ""
"पार्श्वपट्टिकाबटनपङ्क्तयः प्रदर्शनं टॉगल करोति । एषः आदेशः पार्श्वपट्टिकासामग्रीविजेट्-"
"प्रदर्शनं न प्रभावितं करोति, यः कोऽपि पार्श्वपट्टिका दृश्यते सः दृश्यमानः एव तिष्ठति, यदि "
"भवान् तेषां अधः आदेशानां कृते शॉर्टकट् नियुक्तवान् तर्हि अवश्यमेव कार्यं करिष्यति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show <replaceable>Plugin</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>उपकरणदृश्यानि</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> "
"<replaceable>प्लगिन्</replaceable></guimenuitem> दर्शयतु"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A list of all enabled plugins. Use the checkbox in front of each item to "
"toggle the display of the tool view."
msgstr ""
"सर्वेषां सक्षमप्लगिन्स् इत्यस्य सूची । साधनदृश्यस्य प्रदर्शनं टॉग्ल् कर्तुं प्रत्येकस्य द्रव्यस्य पुरतः "
"चेकबॉक्सस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>आदेशपङ्क्तिं प्रति गच्छन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will toggle the display of the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"advanced-editing-tools-commandline.html\">built-in command line</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-commandline.html"
"\">निर्मितस्य आदेशपङ्क्तौ</ulink> इत्यस्य प्रदर्शनं टॉग्ल् करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enlarge Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>फॉन्टं विस्तारयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "This increases the display font size."
msgstr "एतेन प्रदर्शनस्य फ़ॉन्ट् आकारः वर्धते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrink Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>फॉन्टं संकुचितं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid "This decreases the display font size."
msgstr "एतेन प्रदर्शनस्य फ़ॉन्ट् आकारः न्यूनीकरोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Schema</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenu>योजना</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu lists the available color schemes. You can change the schema for "
"the current view here, to change the default schema you need to use the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors\">Fonts "
"&amp; Colors</ulink> page of the config dialog."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् मेन्यू मध्ये उपलब्धानि वर्णयोजनानि सूचीबद्धानि सन्ति । भवान् अत्र वर्तमानदृश्यस्य "
"स्कीमा परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति, पूर्वनिर्धारितं योजनां परिवर्तयितुं भवान् <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors\">Fonts &amp; विन्याससंवादस्य "
"वर्णाः</ulink>पृष्ठम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dynamic Word Wrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>शब्दवेष्टनम्</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>गतिशीलशब्दवेष्टनम् </guimenuitem> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles dynamic word wrap in the current view. Dynamic word wrap makes all "
"the text in a view visible without the need for horizontal scrolling by "
"rendering one actual line on more visual lines as needed."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानदृश्ये गतिशीलशब्दवेष्टनं टॉगल करोति । गतिशीलशब्दवेष्टनम् आवश्यकतानुसारं अधिकदृश्यरेखासु "
"एकां वास्तविकपङ्क्तिं प्रतिपादयित्वा क्षैतिजस्क्रॉलस्य आवश्यकतां विना दृश्ये सर्वं पाठं दृश्यमानं "
"करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Dynamic Word Wrap Indicators</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>शब्दवेष्टनम्</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>गतिशीलशब्दवेष्टनसूचकाः</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when and how the dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed. "
"This is only available if the <guilabel>Dynamic Word Wrap</guilabel> option "
"is checked."
msgstr ""
"गतिशीलशब्दवेष्टनसूचकाः कदा कथं च प्रदर्शितव्याः इति चिनोतु । एतत् केवलं तदा एव उपलब्धं यदा "
"<guilabel>Dynamic Word Wrap</guilabel> विकल्पः परीक्षितः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Static Word Wrap Marker</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>शब्दवेष्टनम्</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>स्थिरशब्दवेष्टनचिह्नं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of a vertical line indicating the position of the wrap "
"width as configured in the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor."
"html#pref-wrap-words-at\">config dialog</ulink>. This feature requires that "
"you use a true fixed-width font."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#pref-wrap-words-at"
"\">config संवाद</ulink इत्यत्र विन्यस्तरूपेण रैपविस्तारस्य स्थानं सूचयन्त्याः ऊर्ध्वाधररेखायाः "
"प्रदर्शनं टॉगलं करोति >। अस्य विशेषतायाः आवश्यकता अस्ति यत् भवान् सत्यं नियत-विस्तार-"
"अक्षरस्य उपयोगं करोतु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>सीमाः</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>चिह्नसीमा दर्शयतु< /गुइमेनुआइटम>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle item. Setting it on checked will make the Icon Border "
"visible in the left side of the active editor, and vice versa. The Icon "
"Border indicates the positions of the marked lines in the editor."
msgstr ""
"एतत् टॉगल-वस्तु अस्ति । चेक्ड् इत्यत्र सेट् करणेन सक्रियसम्पादकस्य वामभागे Icon Border "
"दृश्यमानं भविष्यति, तद्विपरीतम् अपि । Icon Border सम्पादके चिह्नितानां रेखानां स्थानानि "
"सूचयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>सीमाः</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>रेखासङ्ख्याः दर्शयतु< /गुइमेनुआइटम>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle Item. Setting it on checked will make a pane displaying the "
"line numbers of the document visible in the left border of the active "
"editor, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"इदं toggle Item अस्ति। चेक्ड् इत्यत्र सेट् करणेन सक्रियसम्पादकस्य वामसीमायां दस्तावेजस्य "
"रेखासङ्ख्याः प्रदर्शयन्तं फलकं दृश्यते, तद्विपरीतम् अपि ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Marks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>सीमा</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>स्क्रॉलबारचिह्नानि दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the visualization of bookmarks (and other marks) on the vertical "
"scrollbar. When enabled, a mark is represented by a thin line in the mark "
"color at the scrollbar, clicking the &MMB; on the line will scroll the view "
"to a position near the mark."
msgstr ""
"ऊर्ध्वाधरस्क्रॉलबार-उपरि पुस्तकचिह्नानां (अन्यचिह्नानां च) दृश्यीकरणं टॉग्ल् करोति । यदा "
"सक्षमं भवति तदा स्क्रॉलबार इत्यत्र चिह्नवर्णे कृशरेखायाः कृते &MMB; रेखायां दृश्यं चिह्नस्य समीपे "
"स्थाने स्क्रॉल करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Mini-Map</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guisubmenu>सीमा</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>स्क्रॉलबार "
"लघु-नक्शा दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will replace the scrollbar with a visualization of the current "
"document. For more information on the scrollbar minimap, see the <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/kate-part-scrollbar-minimap.html\">Scrollbar Minimap "
"section of the &katepart; Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"एतेन स्क्रॉलबारस्य स्थाने वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य दृश्यीकरणं भविष्यति । स्क्रॉलबार लघुनक्शा विषये "
"अधिकसूचनार्थं &katepart; हस्तपुस्तिका</ulink>।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Code Folding</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सङ्केत तन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options pertain to <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"code-folding.html\">code folding</ulink>:"
msgstr ""
"एते विकल्पाः <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-code-folding."
"html\">कोड् तन्तु</ulink> इत्यस्य सम्बन्धिनो भवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>तन्तुचिह्नानि दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the folding marker pane in the left side of the view."
msgstr "दृश्यस्य वामभागे तन्तुचिह्नफलकस्य प्रदर्शनं टॉगल करोति ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fold Current Node"
msgstr "वर्तमान नोड् गुना"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "यस्मिन् प्रदेशे कर्सरः अस्ति तत् संकुचितं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unfold Current Node"
msgstr "वर्तमान नोड् अनफोल्ड"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "यस्मिन् प्रदेशे कर्सरः अस्ति तस्य विस्तारं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Fold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>शीर्षस्तरीय नोड्स गुना</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collapse all toplevel regions in the document. Click on the right pointing "
"triangle to expand all toplevel regions."
msgstr ""
"दस्तावेजे सर्वाणि शीर्षस्तरीयक्षेत्राणि संकुचयन्तु । सर्वेषां शीर्षस्तरीयक्षेत्राणां विस्तारार्थं "
"दक्षिणसूचकत्रिकोणे नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Unfold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>शीर्षस्तरीयनोड्स अनफोल्ड</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand all toplevel regions in the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजे सर्वाणि शीर्षस्तरीयक्षेत्राणि विस्तारयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Non-Printable Spaces"
msgstr "अमुद्रणयोग्यस्थानानि दर्शयतु"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/hide bounding box around non-printable spaces."
msgstr "अमुद्रणयोग्यस्थानानां परितः बाउण्डिंग् पेटी दर्शयतु/गोपयतु।"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "बुकमार्क मेनू इति"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the entries described here, one entry for each bookmark in the active "
"document will be available. The text will be the first few words of the "
"marked line. Choose an item to move the cursor to the start of that line. "
"The editor will scroll as necessary to make that line visible."
msgstr ""
"अत्र वर्णितप्रविष्टीनां अधः सक्रियदस्तावेजे प्रत्येकं पुस्तकचिह्नस्य कृते एकः प्रविष्टिः उपलभ्यते । "
"पाठः चिह्नितरेखायाः प्रथमाः कतिचन शब्दाः भविष्यन्ति । तस्याः रेखायाः आरम्भे कर्सरं "
"स्थापयितुं एकं द्रव्यं चिनोतु । सम्पादकः तां पङ्क्तिं दृश्यमानं कर्तुं यथावश्यं स्क्रॉल करिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पुस्तकचिह्नानि सेट् कुर्वन्तु</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets or removes a bookmark in the current line of the active document. (If "
"it's there, it is removed, otherwise one is set.)"
msgstr ""
"सक्रियदस्तावेजस्य वर्तमानपङ्क्तौ पुस्तकचिह्नं सेट् करोति अथवा निष्कासयति । (यदि तत्र अस्ति "
"तर्हि निष्कासितम् अन्यथा एकः सेट् भवति।)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear All Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सर्वं पुस्तकचिह्नानि स्वच्छं कुर्वन्तु</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will remove all the markers from the document as well as the "
"list of markers which is appended at the bottom of this menu item."
msgstr ""
"एषः आदेशः दस्तावेजात् सर्वाणि चिह्नानि अपि च चिह्नानां सूचीं निष्कासयिष्यति यत् अस्य मेनू-"
"वस्तूनाम् अधः संलग्नम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>पूर्व</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the first above line with a "
"bookmark. The menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece "
"of text on the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in "
"a line above the cursor."
msgstr ""
"एतेन कर्सरः बुकमार्केन सह प्रथमा उपरि रेखायाः आरम्भं प्रति गमिष्यति । menuitem पाठः "
"रेखासङ्ख्यां रेखायां प्रथमपाठखण्डं च समाविष्टं करिष्यति । एतत् द्रव्यं तदा एव उपलभ्यते यदा "
"कर्सरस्य उपरि रेखायां पुस्तकचिह्नं भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>पुस्तकचिह्नानि</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अनन्तरं</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the next line with a bookmark. The "
"menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece of text on "
"the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in a line "
"below the cursor."
msgstr ""
"एतेन कर्सरः पुस्तकचिह्नसहितं अग्रिमपङ्क्तौ आरम्भं प्रति गमिष्यति । menuitem पाठः रेखासङ्ख्यां "
"रेखायां प्रथमपाठखण्डं च समाविष्टं करिष्यति । एतत् द्रव्यं तदा एव उपलभ्यते यदा कर्सरस्य अधः "
"रेखायां पुस्तकचिह्नं भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1363
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Sessions Menu"
msgstr "सत्रमेनू इति"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains entries for using and managing &kate; sessions. For more "
"information, read <link linkend=\"fundamentals-using-sessions\">Using "
"Sessions</link>."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् मेन्यू मध्ये &amp;kate; सत्रम् । अधिकविवरणार्थं पठन्तु<link linkend="
"\"fundamentals-using-sessions\"> सत्रस्य उपयोगः</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1372
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सत्र</guimenu> <guimenuitem>नव</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new empty session. All currently open files will be closed."
msgstr ""
"नूतनं रिक्तं सत्रं निर्माति । सम्प्रति उद्घाटिताः सर्वाणि सञ्चिकाः पिहिताः भविष्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Session...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सत्र</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सत्रं उद्घाटयतु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open an existing session. The Session Chooser dialog is displayed to let you "
"choose one."
msgstr "विद्यमानं सत्रं उद्घाटयन्तु। एकं चयनं कर्तुं Session Chooser संवादः प्रदर्शितः भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1391
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Quick Open Session</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सत्र</guimenu> <submenu>सत्रं शीघ्रं उद्घाटयतु</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1395
#, no-c-format
msgid "This submenu lets you open an existing session."
msgstr "एतत् उपमेनू भवन्तं विद्यमानं सत्रं उद्घाटयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Session</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सत्र</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सत्रं रक्षतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the current session. If the session is anonymous, you will be prompted "
"for a session name."
msgstr "वर्तमानसत्रं रक्षन्तु। यदि सत्रं अनामिकं भवति तर्हि भवन्तः सत्रनाम प्रार्थयिष्यन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Session As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सत्र</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सत्रं यथा रक्षतु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the current session under a new name. You are prompted for a name to "
"use."
msgstr "वर्तमानसत्रं नूतननाम्ना रक्षन्तु । भवन्तः उपयोक्तुं नाम प्रार्थ्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage Sessions...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सत्र</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सत्रं प्रबन्धयतु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the Session Manager dialog which allows you to rename and delete "
"sessions."
msgstr "Session Manager संवादं प्रदर्शयति यत् सत्रस्य नामकरणं विलोपनं च कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Tools Menu इति"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Read Only Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu> <guimenuitem>केवलपठनविधिः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current document to Read Only mode. This prevents any text addition "
"and any changes in the document formatting."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमानदस्तावेजं Read Only मोड् इत्यत्र सेट् कुर्वन्तु । एतेन किमपि पाठसंयोजनं दस्तावेजस्वरूपणे "
"किमपि परिवर्तनं च निवारितं भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <highsubmenu>मोड्</highsubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the filetype scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/pref-open-save-modes-"
"filetypes.html\">filetype</ulink> mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kate;...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in the Filetypes tab for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"सक्रियदस्तावेजस्य कृते भवता इष्टां सञ्चिकाप्रकारयोजनां चिनोतु । एतेन <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>विन्यासे सेट् कृतं वैश्विकं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/pref-open-save-modes-filetypes.html\">सञ्चिकाप्रकार</ulink> मोडं "
"अधिलिखति &kate;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> केवलं भवतः वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य कृते "
"Filetypes ट्याब् मध्ये ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Highlighting</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>प्रकाशनम्</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the Highlighting scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global highlighting mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"सक्रियदस्तावेजस्य कृते भवन्तः इष्टां Highlighting योजनां चिनोतु । एतेन केवलं भवतः "
"वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य कृते <menuchoice> <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>सम्पादकं "
"विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> इत्यत्र सेट् कृतं वैश्विकं हाइलाइटिङ्ग् मोड् "
"अधिलिखति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Indentation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>इण्डेन्टेशन</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-autoindent.html\">style of "
"indentation</ulink> you want for your active document. This overwrites the "
"global indentation mode set in <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> for "
"your current document only."
msgstr ""
"भवतः सक्रियदस्तावेजस्य कृते इच्छितं <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-autoindent."
"html\">इण्डेन्टेशन</ulink>शैलीं चिनोतु । एतेन केवलं भवतः वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य कृते "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>सम्पादकं विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> इत्यत्र सेट् कृतं वैश्विकं इण्डेन्टेशन मोड् अधिलिखति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>एन्कोडिंग्</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can overwrite the default encoding set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Open/Save</guilabel> page to set a different "
"encoding for your current document. The encoding you set here will be only "
"valid for your current document."
msgstr ""
"सेट् कर्तुं <guilabel>उद्घाटन/रक्षतु</guilabel> पृष्ठे <menuchoice> <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>सम्पादकं विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"इत्यत्र पूर्वनिर्धारितं एन्कोडिंग् सेट् अधिलेखयितुं शक्नुवन्ति भवतः वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य कृते भिन्नं "
"एन्कोडिंग् । भवता अत्र सेट् कृतं एन्कोडिंग् केवलं भवतः वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य कृते मान्यं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1505
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>End of Line</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>पङ्क्तिसमाप्तिः</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. This "
"overwrites the global end of line mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"स्वस्य सक्रियदस्तावेजस्य कृते भवतः इष्टं रेखा-अन्तं चिनोतु । एतेन केवलं भवतः वर्तमानदस्तावेजस्य "
"कृते <menuchoice> <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>सम्पादकं विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> इत्यत्र सेट् कृतं वैश्विकं रेखा मोडं अधिलिखति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Add Byte Mark Order (BOM)</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu> <guisubmenu>बाइट् चिह्नक्रमं (BOM) योजयन्तु</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this action you can explicitly add a byte order mark for unicode "
"encoded documents. The byte order mark (BOM) is a Unicode character used to "
"signal the endianness (byte order) of a text file or stream, for more "
"information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark"
"\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"एतस्य क्रियायाः जाँचं कृत्वा भवान् यूनिकोड एन्कोडेड् दस्तावेजानां कृते स्पष्टतया बाइट् क्रमचिह्नं "
"योजयितुं शक्नोति । बाइट् क्रमचिह्नम् (BOM) एकः यूनिकोड् वर्णः अस्ति यस्य उपयोगः "
"पाठसञ्चिकायाः अथवा धारायाः एण्डियननेस् (बाइट् क्रमः) संकेतयितुं भवति, अधिकसूचनार्थं "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark\" इति पश्यन्तु । "
">बाइटक्रमचिह्न</ulink>।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>स्क्रिप्ट्</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu contains a list of all scripted actions. The list can easily be "
"modified by <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-scripting-"
"command-line\">writing your own scripts</ulink>. This way, &kate; can be "
"extended with user-defined tools."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् उपमेनूमध्ये सर्वेषां स्क्रिप्ट् कृतानां क्रियाणां सूची अस्ति । <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-scripting-command-line\">स्वकीयानि स्क्रिप्ट् "
"लिखित्वा</ulink> इति सूचीं सुलभतया परिवर्तयितुं शक्यते । एवं &कते; उपयोक्तृनिर्धारितसाधनेन "
"विस्तारितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: ulink
#: menus.docbook:1541
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is a complete list of scripts in the &katepart; documentation."
msgstr "&katepart; दस्तावेजीकरणम्।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Invoke Code Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu> <guimenuitem>सङ्केतसमाप्तिम् आह्वयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manually invoke command completion, usually by using a shortcut bound to "
"this action."
msgstr ""
"प्रायः अस्य क्रियायाः बाध्यस्य शॉर्टकट् इत्यस्य उपयोगेन आदेशसमाप्तिः मैन्युअल् रूपेण आह्वयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Word Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>उपकरण</guimenu> <guimenuitem>शब्दसमाप्तिः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Reuse Word Below</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) and <guimenuitem>Reuse Word Above</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>8</keycap></"
"keycombo>) complete the currently typed text by searching for similar words "
"backward or forward from the current cursor position. <guimenuitem>Shell "
"Completion</guimenuitem> pops up a completion box with matching entries."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>अधः शब्दस्य पुनः प्रयोगः</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) तथा <guimenuitem>उपरि शब्दस्य पुनः "
"प्रयोगः</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action= \"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>8</keycap></"
"keycombo>) पृष्ठतः अथवा समानशब्दान् अन्वेष्य सम्प्रति टङ्कितं पाठं पूर्णं कुर्वन्तु वर्तमान "
"कर्सरस्थानात् अग्रे । <guimenuitem>Shell Completion</guimenuitem> इत्यनेन मेलप्रविष्टैः "
"सह समाप्तिपेटिकां पोप् अप भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>वर्तनी</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> स्वचालितं वर्तनीपरीक्षा</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem> is enabled, wrongly "
"spelled text is underlined in the document on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"यदा <guimenuitem>स्वचालितं वर्तनीपरीक्षा</guimenuitem> सक्षमं भवति तदा दस्तावेजे "
"उड्डयनसमये गलत् वर्तनीयुक्तः पाठः रेखांकितः भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>वर्तनी</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>वर्तनी..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program - a program designed to help the "
"user catch and correct any spelling errors."
msgstr ""
"एतेन वर्तनीपरीक्षणकार्यक्रमः आरभ्यते - एषः कार्यक्रमः यः उपयोक्तुः वर्तनीदोषान् गृहीतुं सम्यक् "
"कर्तुं च सहायं कर्तुं विनिर्मितः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on how to use the &kde; spellchecking program, see the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/spellcheck.html\"><emphasis>Check Spelling</"
"emphasis> section of the <emphasis>&kde; Fundamentals</emphasis> "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kde; वर्तनीपरीक्षणकार्यक्रमः, <emphasis>&kde; मूलभूत</emphasis> दस्तावेजीकरणं</"
"ulink>।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu> <guisubmenu>वर्तनी</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>वर्तनी "
"(कर्सरतः)...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program but it starts where your cursor is "
"instead of at the beginning of the document."
msgstr ""
"एतेन वर्तनीपरीक्षाकार्यक्रमः आरभ्यते परन्तु दस्तावेजस्य आरम्भे न अपितु यत्र भवतः कर्सरः अस्ति "
"तत्र आरभ्यते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>उपकरणाः</guimenu> <guisubmenu>वर्तनी</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>वर्तनीपरीक्षणचयनम्...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellchecks the current selection."
msgstr "वर्तमानचयनस्य वर्तनीपरीक्षां करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Dictionary</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>उपकरणं</guimenu> <guisubmenu>वर्तनी</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>शब्दकोशं "
"परिवर्तयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a drop down box with all available dictionaries for spellchecking "
"at the bottom of the editor window. This allows easy switching of the "
"spellcheck dictionary &eg; for automatic spellcheck of text in different "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"सम्पादकविण्डो इत्यस्य अधः वर्तनीपरीक्षायै सर्वैः उपलब्धैः शब्दकोशैः सह एकं ड्रॉप् डाउन पेटी "
"प्रदर्शयति । एतेन वर्तनीपरीक्षा शब्दकोशस्य सुलभं परिवर्तनं भवति &eg; विभिन्नभाषासु पाठस्य "
"स्वचालितवर्तनीपरीक्षायै।"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1806
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "सेटिंग्स् एण्ड् हेल्प् मेन्यू"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections about the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> "
"and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</"
"ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals with these additional entries:"
msgstr ""
"&कते; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा <guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-"
"वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /ulink> तथा च &kde; एतेषां "
"अतिरिक्तप्रविष्टीनां सह मौलिकाः :"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1817
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Color Theme</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>रङ्गविषयः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use a different color scheme from the system’s global color schemes "
"described in the &systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors/"
"index.html\">Colors</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors/index.html"
"\">रङ्गाः</ulink> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1827
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Tabs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ट्याब्स् दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1831
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tabs are moveable using the &LMB; and have actions in the context menu to "
"close documents, copy the path to the clipboard or open the folder of the "
"document in the filemanager. Using the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"quickopen-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"view-"
"quick-open\"><guibutton>Quick Open</guibutton> </link> button makes "
"switching between documents easy. Click the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-split-left-"
"right-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"with the &LMB; to open a menu with actions from the <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"ट्याब्स् &amp;LMB; तथा च दस्तावेजान् बन्दं कर्तुं, क्लिप्बोर्ड् प्रति मार्गं प्रतिलिखितुं वा "
"सञ्चिकाप्रबन्धके दस्तावेजस्य पुटं उद्घाटयितुं सन्दर्भमेनूमध्ये क्रियाः सन्ति । प्रयुज्य "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"quickopen-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><link linkend=\"view-quick-"
"open\"><guibutton> त्वरित उद्घाटनम्</guibutton></link> button इत्यनेन दस्तावेजानां "
"मध्ये स्विचिंग् सुलभं भवति । क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"view-split-left-right-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> बटनं &amp;LMB; तः क्रियाभिः सह मेनू उद्घाटयितुं<guimenu> दृश्यं</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu> विभक्त दृश्य</guisubmenu> मेनू।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Path in Titlebar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>शीर्षकपट्टिकायां मार्गं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1845
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled the full path of the active document is displayed, otherwise only "
"the filename. This is useful if you edit several files with the same "
"filename to distinguish them."
msgstr ""
"यदि सक्षमं भवति तर्हि सक्रियदस्तावेजस्य पूर्णमार्गः प्रदर्शितः भवति, अन्यथा केवलं सञ्चिकानाम "
"। यदि भवान् समानसञ्चिकानाम्ना अनेकसञ्चिकाः सम्पादयति तर्हि एतत् उपयोगी भवति ।"
